reviewText: Used it and it was great

I had always used just a cleaning tape for VHS. Put it in, run it for a few seconds and its done. I didn't realize what I was getting here, having to fill with ink and it takes awhile to run through. Tapes worked for a short while and had to use again. Not sure if it is the tape player or this cleaning tape.
I sure wish I knew how this product worked because I never received it...I gave it one star because I had to...Not because I wanted to....Enough said!
